                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The pylons caught your silhouette two towers back. I read the grid, and the grid read you. Nobody crosses Pylon Path unlogged."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Cyber City is past the substation and Volt holds the Electric gym there - he never stops talking once he starts. Face me first or pay the crossing."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "This corridor carries more current than it should lately. I watch it so trainers bound for Cyber do not become part of the load. Battle me, or square the toll and go."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The old plate-reader by the substation says the overload is upstream. It is downstream. Trust the one who climbs the towers in gloves, not the one who reads about them in the shade."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Line Tech Volta",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
